    • 方法详细资料

      • Make

        public GeoRegion Make(Point2D[] Points)
        构造简单线对象
        参数:
        Points - 点串数组(地图坐标)
        返回:
        返回面对象
        示例代码:
          Point2D[] pnts = new Point2D[10];
          Point2D p2D = new Point2D();
          p2D = m_mapView.GetCenter();
          Point2D[] pnts = new Point2D[10];
          for(int i=0;i'<'pnts.length;i++){
              pnts[i] = new Point2D();
              pnts[i].x = p2D.x + i*0.00001;
              pnts[i].y = p2D.y + i*0.00001;
          }
          GeoRegion gRegion = new GeoRegion();
          gRegion.Make(pnts);
          int nCount = gRegion.GetPointCount();

      • MakeWithSub

        public GeoRegion MakeWithSub(Point2D[] Points,
                    int[] pSubPntCounts)
        构造带有子对象的面对象
        参数:
        Points - 点串数组
        pSubPntCounts - 子对象节点数数组
        返回:
        返回面对象
        示例代码:
          Point2D[] pnts = new Point2D[10];
          Point2D p2D = new Point2D();
          p2D = m_mapView.GetCenter();
          Point2D[] pnts = new Point2D[10];
          for(int i=0;i'<'pnts.length;i++){
              pnts[i] = new Point2D();
              pnts[i].x = p2D.x + i*0.00001;
              pnts[i].y = p2D.y + i*0.00001;
          }
          int[] nSubPnts={3,3,4};
          GeoRegion gRegion = new GeoRegion();
          gRegion.MakeWithSub(pnts,nSubPnts);
          int nCount = gRegion.GetSubCount();    //获取子对象个数
          nCount = gRegion.GetSubPntCount(0);    //获取第一个子对象节点数目

      • GetPoints

        public Point2D[] GetPoints(int nSubIndex)
        获取面对象节点数据
        参数:
        nSubIndex - 子对象序号,如无子对象nSubIndex为0
        返回:
        返回(子)对象节点数组
        示例代码:
          Point2D[] pnts = new Point2D[10];
          for(int i=0;i'<'10;i++){
              pnts[i] = new Point2D();
          }
          pnts = gRegion.GetPoints(0);
